  $ hg book -d scratch/serverbranch
  abort: scratch bookmark 'scratch/serverbranch' does not exist in path 'default'
  [255]
  $ hg book --remote

Test deleting a local bookmark that has a scratch-like name
  $ hg book scratch/thisisalocalbm
  $ hg book
